                            <comment id="13012165" author="hudson" created="Mon, 28 Mar 2011 18:16:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.7 #410 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.7/410/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.7/410/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
